---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Timeline from '../components/Timeline.astro'

const pageTitle = "afrizal's website";
---
<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <div class="gif">
        <img width="300" height="259" alt="RaccoonSpaceGif" src="/giphy.webp"/>
    </div>
    <h1>Afrizal</h1>
    <small>Math student</small>
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>
        Hello! I'm Muhammad <b>Afrizal</b>, a passionate student majoring in Mathematics with a keen interest in programming. I have always been fascinated by the world of coding, and I've taken it upon myself to dive into the realm of self-taught programming. My educational journey began in a vocational high school where I specialized in software engineering, which laid a strong foundation for my programming skills.
    </p>
    <p>
        Currently, my focus is on the exciting and rapidly evolving field of data science and machine learning. I believe that harnessing the power of data can unlock countless possibilities and insights. Through my personal website, I aim to share my experiences, projects, and knowledge gained on this exciting journey. Join me as I explore the endless possibilities of mathematics, programming, and the fascinating world of data!
    </p>
    <div class="button">
        <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1o7IQxOzupT09YTIGr-heJjj1EYWudlCJ/view?usp=sharing" target="_blank">
            <button>CV</button>
        </a>
    </div>

    <h2>Academics</h2>
    <Timeline />
    <h2>Skills</h2>
    <div class="link-images">
       
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="Docker" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/pandas/pandas-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="Docker" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/docker/docker-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="HTML5" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/html5/html5-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="Javascript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/javascript/javascript-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="CSS" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/css3/css3-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="Jupyter Notebook" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/jupyter/jupyter-original-wordmark.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="MySQL" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/mysql/mysql-original-wordmark.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="NodeJS" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/nodejs/nodejs-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="MySQL" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/numpy/numpy-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="PostGres" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/postgresql/postgresql-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="PostGres" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/postgresql/postgresql-plain.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="PostGres" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/python/python-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="PostGres" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/r/r-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="PostGres" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/flask/flask-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="PostGres" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/express/express-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="PostGres" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/git/git-original.svg"/>
        <img width="46" height="46" alt="PostGres" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/go/go-original.svg"/>
    </div>
    <h2>Interests</h2>
    <p>
        I'm passionate about programming, philosophy, and the fascinating world of data. The art of coding allows me to create, innovate, and solve complex problems, while philosophy helps me ponder life's fundamental questions. Currently, I'm immersing myself in data science and machine learning, driven by the belief that data holds the key to unlocking insights and making meaningful advancements in today's technology-driven world.
    </p>
</Layout>
<style>
    /* small */
    small {
        background-color: #584966;
        color: #fdebf3;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-family: 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.3em 0.6em 0.2em;
    }

    /* Button */
    button {
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0);
        border: 2px solid #78c2ad;
        border-radius: 8px;
        color: #78c2ad;
        font: 600 16px 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
        padding: 8px 16px;
        transition: background-color 0.4s, color 0.4s;
    }

    button:hover {
        background-color: #78c2ad;
        color: #fdebf3;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    .button {
        text-align: center;
    }

    /* Skill images */
    .link-images img {
        margin: 16px 4px;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .link-images img {
            height: 30px;
            width: 30px;
            margin: 16px 1px;
        }
    }
</style>
